author: @luxgoods
content: This is a joke. The government and a private bank has paid her 15 millions pounds for this show, whilst down in the south of Brazil the flood is still destroying thousands of lives of the less fortunate. Please check what’s happening at Rio Grande do Sul state, which in fact it’s one of the most beautiful regions in Brazil, now destroyed!
